TurbMoore80Red algorithm

Applies the TurbMoore80Red algorithm

TurbMoore80Red(w658)

Arguments

w658

numeric. Value at wavelength of 658 nm

Value

RasterLayer or numeric

References

Moore, G.K., Satellite remote sensing of water turbidity, Hydrological Sciences, 1980, 25, 4, 407-422.
